        "client_msg_id": "B44B517F-17D5-49A3-BDD6-377AAE386381",
        "text": "On the subject of order-of-magnitude decreases in costs, Alan Kay’s discussion of “better old thing” vs. “brand new thing” (~27:00): <https:\/\/youtu.be\/oKg1hTOQXoY?si=Z8C4WCgYNiXtHKl6|https:\/\/youtu.be\/oKg1hTOQXoY?si=Z8C4WCgYNiXtHKl6>\nAnd I can’t find what talk I’m thinking of but I’ve definitely seen a talk before that framed order of magnitude improvements in performance as new features\/capabilities. Might’ve been Gary Bernhardt.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "8ca6563fd00d",
