                                "text": "\nAnd "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "I can’t find what talk I’m thinking of but I’ve definitely seen a talk before that framed order of magnitude improvements in performance as new features\/capabilities. Might’ve been Gary Bernhardt."
